InsProductAsyncRatingService Methods

These are the available InsProductAsyncRatingService methods.

InsProductAsyncRatingService:fetchProductsPrice
Use this service to fetch asynchronous rating results.
InsProductAsyncRatingService:fetchRepriceProductPrice
Use this service to fetch asynchronous rating results for a reprice product request.
InsProductAsyncRatingService:repriceProduct
Asynchronously recalculate the price of a product based on selectedProduct JSON and userInput.
InsProductAsyncRatingService:startAsyncRating
Asynchronously calculate product prices based on a list of product IDs.
